    "The product represents the estimated mediated effect on the dependent variable.",
    "We compute confidence intervals based on these resampled values.",
    "If zero is not included in the confidence interval, the path is significant at a 95% confidence level.",
    "Full mediation is supported when only the average causal mediation effect is significant.",
    "The mediation is partial when the average causal mediation effect and the direct effect are both significant."
